Usage: uiGetRecordObjByInfo [-help] [-layer <string>] [-name <string>]
                            -objType {viaInst sViaInst sWire wire pWire pBlkg}
                            -rect {x1 y1 x2 y2}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-layer <string>         # Z Value of Layer or Layer Range (string, optional)
-name <string>          # Name of Object or Net Name of Routing Object
                        # (string, optional)
-objType {viaInst sViaInst sWire wire pWire pBlkg}
                        # Object Type (enum, required)
-rect {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Object Bounding Box (box, required)